Use Cases :

Learner:
 - update course progress
 - view course details
 - add,view comments
 - unenroll course
 - rate course
 - enroll new course

Creator:
 - view created courses
 - change course name
 - change course price
 - add/remove course category
 - edit course content
 - view comments
 - delete course
 - add new course

Admin:
 - remove learner/creator
 - change learner/creator/admin password
 - add/remove Zcourse Courses categories
 - view all courses
 - delete any course